---
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>About · Aicha on AI & Education</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0f172a;
        --surface: #1e293b;
        --text: #f8fafc;
        --text-muted: #94a3b8;
        --accent: #38bdf8;
        --border: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.15);
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.8;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }
      .site-header {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        z-index: 100;
      }
      .header-inner {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .logo {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .logo span { color: var(--accent); }
      .nav-links a {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-left: 2rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
      .container {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
      }
      .about-header {
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }
      .about-header h1 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .about-header p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      .content-block {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      .content-block h2 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--accent);
      }
      .content-block p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .content-block p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
      .content-block ul {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
      }
      .content-block li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .site-footer {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .nav-links { display: none; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <div class="header-inner">
        <a href="/" class="logo">Aicha<span>.</span></a>
        <nav class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">Articles</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
      <div class="about-header">
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p>AI-Driven Education Analyst focused on workforce transformation</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Who I Am</h2>
        <p>I am Aicha Marrhich, an AI-Driven Education Analyst. I synthesize research from leading institutions — NBER, arXiv, and beyond — to make complex AI trends actionable for educators, strategists, and professionals.</p>
        <p>My work bridges the gap between academic research and practical workforce strategy.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>What I Cover</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>AI's real impact on jobs and productivity</li>
          <li>How education systems must adapt to technological shifts</li>
          <li>Workforce strategy and talent development</li>
          <li>The "seniority gradient" and early-career pathways</li>
          <li>Growth-focused vs. cost-cutting AI implementation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Connect</h2>
        <p>Follow my research briefs here or connect with me on LinkedIn to discuss AI, education, and the future of work.</p>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <p>© 2026 Aicha Marrhich · Built with Astro</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
